					mod: 'quote-lisa-2',
					img: 'user-16-100x100',
					text: 'Following the delivery and set-up of my new dining room furniture today, I would like to thank your friendly team for their courteous manner and arriving within the time limit set when I was called earlier this morning. This is my 1st purchase with you, and it was a great experience. I wil definitely recommend you to my friends.',
					author: 'Catherine Williams',
					status: 'Local shop owner'
				})
				+quote-lisa({
					mod: 'quote-lisa-2',
					img: 'user-17-100x100',
					text: 'Your team provided excellent service service today. Everything arrived on time and I was informed of your deliverers’ ETA. I was extra happy as I am wheelchair user and they went extra mile to make me happy by even putting my heavy mattress onto the bed afterwards which was in storage in my shed. Thank you!',
					author: 'Rupert Wood',
					status: 'House owner'
				})
				+quote-lisa({
					mod: 'quote-lisa-2',
					img: 'user-19-100x100',
